metadata.name: Through My Eyes
metadata.description:
Poombarai is a small village in Kodaikanal, Tamilnadu, India. I had visited this place in 2014. I happened to see this boy.  His face and eyes are mesmerizing. I wanted to take a portrait of him. I asked him for permission to take a portrait. I took a few portraits of him and this one came out well. 

International Awards

Prix de la Photographie Paris (Px3) 2014 - Silver Award in Portraiture/Children
ND Awards 2014 - Honorable Mention
Shoot The Face April 2014 - Finalist

Artist: - Mahesh Balasubramanian

Edition: 1/1
Date: 22-Feb-2014
Dimensions: 5203 x 3469, 300 DPI
